com.misc.common.moplaf.propagator

Class PropagatorAbstractAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.AdapterImpl
      • com.misc.common.moplaf.propagator.AbstractAdapter
        • com.misc.common.moplaf.propagator.PropagatorAbstractAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Adapter, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Adapter.Internal
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PropagatorDependencyAdapter, PropagatorFunctionAdapter

    public class PropagatorAbstractAdapter
extends AbstractAdapter
    The base class of the Adapters used by the Propagator framework. Listens to notifications and triggers changes by calling touch().

    Implement some convenience methods such as

    • AbstractAdapter.isFeatureChanged(Notification, Object): if some EMF feature is changed
    • AbstractAdapter.isListFeatureAddedRemoved(Notification, Object): if some reference is added/removed

    Delegate listening to a collection of listeners (target object of this propagator) or to PropagatorDependencyAdapters (other emf objects naviguable from the target object of this propagator).

    Two standard Listeners are provided. A PropagatorAbstractAdapter.FeatureListener, listening to changes of some feature of this propagator's Notifier and a PropagatorAbstractAdapter.NavigationFeatureListener, listening to changes of some reference held by this propagator's Notifier, and allowing to listen to changes in the referred object by receiving a PropagatorDependencyAdapter. These standards Listeners can be added with the convenience methods addFeatureListener(Object) and addNavigationFeatureListener(Object, Object) respectively.

    Registering the PropagatorDependencyAdapters is done by the method PropagatorAbstractAdapter.Listener.addPropagatorFunctionAdapters(), called when this adapter is added to the notifier. Unregistering the PropagatorDependencyAdapters is done by the method PropagatorAbstractAdapter.Listener.disposePropagatorFunctionAdapters(), called when the adapter is removed from the Notifier.

    Unregistering the propagatorFunctionAdapters is done by the method disposePropagatorFunctionAdapters().

    michel
